ber 10th, commemorates the adoption of the Universal Declaration of Human Rights (UDHR) by the United Nations General Assembly in 1948. It serves as a poignant reminder of the importance of upholding and promoting the fundamental rights and dignity of all individuals worldwide. In this blog, we'll explore the significance of Human Rights Day, how it engages learners, and highlight organisations providing support in this crucial endeavour, including The Mandatory Training Group, a leading UK provider of Human Rights Day-related content.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-7709_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-7710_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-7711_">Definitions</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/protest-placard-39-freedom-is-a-human-right-39-2023-11-27-05-26-15-utc.jpg?v=1709295871" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/protest-placard-39-freedom-is-a-human-right-39-2023-11-27-05-26-15-utc.jpg?v=1709295871 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="From Awareness to Action: Engaging Learners in Human Rights Advocacy Courses - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="From Awareness to Action: Engaging Learners in Human Rights Advocacy Courses - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-7713_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-7714_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by FabrikaPhoto via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-7716_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="L